/-- A limit (over a general filter) of measurable `в„қвүҘ0`-valued functions is measurable. -/
theorem measurable_of_tendsto' {О№} {f : О№ вҶ’ Оұ вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0} {g : Оұ вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0} (u : Filter О№) [NeBot u]
